{"tid":220044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話大部份人反對近親亂倫,請進","createTime":"2017-04-27T16:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T10:50:44.000Z","uid":4672,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"202cd7596c672c184751b5fa729b00a24070cdc4","tid":220044,"uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7b612w4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7b612w4.jpg&h=1eb9931f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點啊 有冇影響社會風氣啊？<br />\n<br />\n有冇每日頭條都係強姦親戚啊？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黎駁啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f8912078be1ff91dbf5e9e32b93a0919f302383","tid":220044,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"wiki ： 近親婚姻"},{"pid":"9fb98b6fc55efa32c5c746acdb3268aece3c1ca1","tid":220044,"uid":21896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:16:55.000Z","msg":"講真，連登班廢柴邊答到你呀，建議樓主唔好再開post,聽日一於響銅鑼灣開個街站同人討論好過啦，再唔係上城市論壇討論，咁樣有意義好多架<br />\n好過對住連登班垃圾啦"},{"pid":"5f4f51f384fcbad651fc8bb09eda7f7be9a5de18","tid":220044,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"個人認為華人社會強調倫理"},{"pid":"b8adc813dd74d9cd65e33e1f7a6b5e2ab09c3052","tid":220044,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26a40be3b94c2e279499d356a8c62c9cff9b5f5e","tid":220044,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>堂表兄弟姊妹包括晒所有亂倫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係血緣相似度12.5% ，25% 同50% 呢d數字分別<br />\n<br />\n本質上亂倫就係亂倫 <br />\n<br />\n如果12.5%得 點解25%唔得？"},{"pid":"8260fc29a740dc81cce72b678f646b0f5ff742ac","tid":220044,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，連登班廢柴邊答到你呀，